high_descs: grab the cloth on the left
turn around, walk to the sink on the right
put the cloth in the sink, wash the cloth with water, take the cloth out
turn around, walk to the toilet,
put the cloth on the toilet
anns.task_desc: wash the cloth in the sink, put the cloth on the toilet

high_descs: Turn around to your right then face the tub
Pick up the dirty cloth close to the faucet
Turn around to your left move forward then turn right
Put the dirty cloth on the sink and rinse it
Turn around to your left walk towards the right side of the toilet tank then face left
Put the clean cloth on the tank beside the dirty cloth
anns.task_desc: Clean the dirty cloth, put it on the tank

high_descs: Turn around to face the bathtub.
Get the red washcloth that is near the faucet on the left.
Go to the sink to your left.
Rinse the washcloth in the sink.
Turn left to face the opposite direction, then go forward to the right side of the toilet and turn to face the side of the toilet.
Put the washcloth on the back of the tank, between the other washcloth and the wall.
anns.task_desc: Move a cleaned washcloth to the back of the toilet tank.
